<main class="main-content">
  <section id="hero" class="section hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to HST Fundings</h1>
      <p>Your trusted partner for unsecured business loans. SMB Funding in Canada & USA. Get funds for your small business in just 24 hours. HST Funding is dedicated to helping your small or mid-sized business succeed by providing quick, easy small business funding in as little as one business day. We provide alternative business funding from as low as $5,000 up to $500,000 in all industries across Canada & USA.</p>
